-- Obama to Nominate Mayor Foxx to Head Transportation Department
-- B y   R o g e r   R u n n i n g e n
-- 2013-04-28T20:53:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-28/obama-to-nominate-mayor-foxx-to-head-transportation-department.html
President  Barack Obama  will
nominate Charlotte, North Carolina, Mayor Anthony Foxx to be the
next Secretary of Transportation, according to a White House
official who spoke on condition of anonymity.  Obama will announce the nomination tomorrow, the official
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Roger Runningen in Washington at 
 rrunningen@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
